---
title: Maple-Thyme Pork Burgers with Potato Wedges and Kale-Apple Salad
description: Breakfast sausage flavours in a homemade burger patty. Top burgers with a fried egg to dig into a brunch vibe. Dip golden potato wedges in zesty mayo dip!
